# UHC
- [ ] TP logic on start
- [ ] Teams pre made or random or on meetup
- [ ] AFK for players
- [ ] Border shrink
- [ ] Final heal and boost
- [ ] Win detection
- [ ] Configuration policies with binary encoding


# Functions

| function     | desc                                                                                                                                       | runs_on                   | condition |
| ------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------- | --------- |
| waiting      | setea efectos y valors default de scoreboards para todos los players                                                                       | every tick                | status=0  |
| start        | Hace los tps, armas los equipos random (if needed) reactiva las gamerules y limpia los scoreboards (jic) y setea el status a 1 (playing)   | trigger by admin to start |           |
| setup        | gamerules para mantener el world estatico, worldborder y crea los scoreboards (triggers too)                                               | initial                   |           |
| death        | Depende en el contador de muertes, cuando es 1 se setea a espectador y spawnea el loop (player head) y se setea el contador de muertes a 2 | everytick                 | dead=1    |
| win          |                                                                                                                                            |                           |           |
| final_battle |                                                                                                                                            |                           |           |
| enable_pvp   |                                                                                                                                            |                           |           |

# Scoreboards

| name   | intial | description       | chanes_on      |
| ------ | ------ | ----------------- | -------------- |
| status | 0      | status scoreboard | function start |
| dead   |        |                   |                |
| kills  |        |                   |                |
| id     |        |                   |                |
| team   |        |                   |                |
| alive_players   |0|count of players alive, sets to active players on started|started,death,revive|

# Status

| status       | value | description                                | changes_on         |
| ------------ | ----- | ------------------------------------------ | ------------------ |
| waiting      | 0     | Waiting for all palyers to be on and start | initial            |
| no_pvp       | 1     | No pvp time for initial prep               | function start     |
| pvp          | 2     | After x time pvp is enabled                | pvp_timer          |
| final_battle | 3     | Shrinks                                    | timer              |
| ended        | 4     |                                            | only 1 player left (alive_players = 1) |
